notes.title: Burna Boy Album
notes.details: I Told Them... is the seventh studio album by Nigerian singer Burna Boy. It was released on 25 August 2023 through Atlantic, Spaceship Records, and Bad Habit. The album features guest appearances from 21 Savage, Dave, Seyi Vibez, J. Cole, GZA and RZA of the Wu-Tang Clan, and Byron Messia.
